\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Desert skies are such a deep bue because desert air is unnaturally pure, free of floating partics and droplets call aerosols. These fill the sky with white ight, diluting the blue. }
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
